7. Cigar:swisher == Color:lavender
8. Beverage:sprite is in the middle
9. Nationality:dutch is on the far left
10. Cigar:game is on the left or right of Pet:hedgehog
11. Cigar:swisher is to the left or right of Pet:snake
12. Cigar:siglo == Beverage:lemonade
13. Nationality:italian == Cigar:bolivar
14. Nationality:dutch is to the left or right of Color:blood-red

